What can you do?

You can make a difference!

With a donation of $35 we can provide an adult with a consultation, including medication and laboratory tests. For $285 you can cover a patient's overnight stay in our inpatient ward. By 2025, the hospital expects to provide approximately 3,300 adult consultations and 720 overnight stays annually.

If you choose to become a regular donor, we can better ensure the continuity of this vital care in Putumayo.
{% image src="/media/2024/11/2023.07.27-patient-consult-with-Carolien.IMG_3085.jpg" align="center" /%}


On GivingTuesday, we can work together to make the world a little better for the people of Putumayo!

